.data-card .number {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #00d4ff;
}

.data-card .label {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: #94a3b8;
  margin-top: 4px;
}
```

### 4.5 表格组件
```css
table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin: 16px 0;
}

th {
  background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1);
  color: #00d4ff;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
}

td {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  color: #94a3b8;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}

tr:hover td {
  background: rgba(0,212,255,0.05);
}
```

